data.description: PRICE REDUCED. Beautiful newer home in a secluded and quiet gated community. Close up mountain views are spectacular from the front courtyard and the back patios. Beautiful kitchen with Granite countertops throughout the home. Great room concept. Split bedroom floorplan with large master bedroom and closet. Expanded Laundry room with loads of storage.. Open space behind home. Rec center on-site with an enormous pool, spa, tennis, pickleball and more. Bonus: Almost new private spa off the master bedroom.  Enjoy already maturing citrus trees: Meyer Lemon, Lime and a Sweet Orange. Some furnishings may be available for sale. Need closing to take place after April 8. UPDATE: Seller offers a $5K paint allowance at closing to repaint the interior of the home to your liking.
